Supress daily DMARC reports
--------------------------------

eFa sends daily DMARC reports to suppress or disable this

# vim /etc/sysconfig/eFa-Daily-DMARC

SENDREPORTS="no"


Quarantine full mail with queue
--------------------------------

# vi /etc/MailScanner/MailScanner.conf

Deliver Cleaned Messages = no      [ may set 'yes' on situation ]
Quarantine Whole Message = yes
Quarantine Whole Messages As Queue Files = yes
